  - Game-changing ideas and innovations
  - Never-seen-before features
  - Features that make apps industry-leading

## Quality Control Scoring

**Minimum Score: 90/100 Required**

Scoring breakdown:
- Visual Design & Dopamine UX: 25 points
- Functionality & Completeness: 25 points
- Performance & Optimization: 15 points
- User Experience & Usability: 15 points
- Innovation & Game-Changing Features: 10 points
- Code Quality & Architecture: 10 points

See QUALITY_CONTROL.md for detailed scoring criteria.

