## Completion Requirements

- **Never move to next app until current app scores 90+**
- **100% completion** required - all tasks at highest quality
- Rigorous executive quality control standards
- Minor adjustments/improvements are approved and encouraged
- Some apps may need nothing or minor tweaks - that's fine

## App Purpose

Every app must do its intended purpose **exceptionally well**. If it doesn't serve its purpose perfectly, it's not ready. Apps must be game-changing, top-tier, and never-seen-before quality.
